# 20.Multi-Currency Exchange Desk
#Context
#Foreign exchange and e-commerce platforms must handle conversions between multiple currencies. This task involves creating a simple tool that uses predefined exchange rates to perform these conversions

EUR = 1.18
USD = 1.27 
JPY = 191.50

gbp = float(input('enter an amount in GBP: '))
print(f"{gbp} is equivalent to {round (EUR * gbp)} EUR, {round (USD*gbp)} USD, {round (JPY*gbp)} JPY")

